Technosub will be attending a series of industry events this year to showcase its portfolio of pumping solutions. Please find further details for forthcoming shows below: May Technosub will participate in the of the Canadian Mining Institute convention, which will be held in Vancouver at its Vancouver Convention Center. June Technosub will be exhibiting at the Northern Mines Expo at Timmins McIntyre Community Center. Technosub will be exhibiting at the Global Petroleum Show, that will take place in Calgary at Stampede Park. September Technosub will be present at the North American Mining Expo (N.A.M.E.) , which will be held in Hanmer (Sudbury, ON) at the Centennial Community Center. For more information, please contact Technosub.